    "Five uncalibrated human videos (3-4 seconds each) are captured per task using a handheld phone.",
    "These clips differ substantially from the robot setting in background, lighting, embodiment, and object placement.",
    "Each figure below shows all warmup demonstrations for the four tasks (Clothes, Block, Brush, Ball).",
    "For each demo, the top row displays the first frame and the bottom row displays the final frame.",
    "Long horizon experimentsTo assess whether TraceGen's predicted trace can be composed into longer multi-step behaviors, we evaluate the model on a long-horizon Sorting task."
